title: Anti NWO Exposing Dutch Government Cover Up.mp4
description:
The Dutch government have covered up a
massive security breach since June 2011

The security breach affected the satellite communications of the following
organisations...

1) European Commission sites all over the world.
2) United Nations Development program sites all over the world.
3) The World Health Organisation sites all over the world.
4) The private calls of British soldiers in Iraq and Afghanistan.
5) The private calls of American soldiers in Iraq and Afghanistan.

Short movie with the details.
